reviewText: I liked this show but the item i received was in used and not new so i had to return it.
Really was a good title can be good for a dub.  Has some good ideas here.

From the guys that made Mobil suit gundam, it is pretty good only problem is it's listed with an English dub but it doesn't have it it's more then likely a mistake on Amazon for listing it like that but other then that it's a good show if you like gundam

Really good series. If you like mecha anime at all, you should give this a shot.
You may ask why I am giving it a 4? Well, the packaging says that it is dubbed, but it actually isn't.
It says that it is dubbed in english but it is not.
This is a great series the story is original. I could't stop watching until the end.
Great show but confused haven't opened this yet. The box says its in Japanese but the description says dubbed in English. Which is it???

This for being kind of similar to Gundam I kind of like it, but it call Buddy Complex it's a show, if your a fan of mecha then this is a good show to watch if your new and you want to give it a try then watch the 2 episodes you would definitely like it.
